OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry to start
OL,6,Fthe evening, though largely cloudy.
OL,7,FOutbreaks of light rain will move west
OL,8,Fovernight. Some clear spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping in the west late in the
OL,10,Fnight. Winds generally light, though
OL,11,Fbreezy along the coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FSome occasional bright spells
OL,14,Fthrough the morning. Occasional heavy
OL,15,Fshowers developing during the
OL,16,Fafternoon, with a chance of thunder.
OL,17,FLow cloud increasing overnight.
OL,18,FTemperatures around average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
